      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a driver-focused example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, with the double VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Power is sent through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's known structural stress points. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including a cooling system overhaul and rod bearing inspection\u2014are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, high-revving analogue experience.",
